reviews.text: I would give this 0 stars if I could. We were called in by a promoter. We sat down and ordered food. 30 minutes later when we asked how long it would the same waitress acted like she didn't know we ordered. Then she told us the things we wanted we're not available. Also during the 30 minute (or more) wait, I ordered still water. She brought sparkling without telling me why. When I finally caught her attention again she told me they were out of still water.

Never never go here, they will charge you huge money! Everytime you order, they give a bill and you pay for it. At the end, they will charge you all over the bill again. And threaten you.  Or when they give back the change they give less back on purpose.
Very bad attitude
Dishonest people. Quoted me 500 HKD for a 2 liter jug when it would cost me just over 300 for 4 pints. Always check prices first
The owner was extremely aggressive and argumentative. Tried to hit me. Will never visit again! Do not recommend!

The people were nice, drinks a decent price, and the waitress Xiumin was super friendly and cute! She was so into the music she danced while she served tables! It was so fun it got me to start feeling the music!!
